title: Early Bill Maher
description:
The greatest stand-up comics, (Pryor, Carlin, Bruce, Rock, Maher, Hicks, Chappelle, etc.), are brilliant because they tell the truth, yet they make us laugh. Y'all loved my Chris Rock upload, so here's Bill Maher.  This torrent includes One Night Stand, (1989), Be More Cynical, (2000), Victory Begins at Home, (2003), I'm Swiss, (2005), The Decider, (2007), & But I'm Not Wrong, (2010.)

As always, support the artist by buying their work.

Please help me, as I'm new to this business of uploading torrents, by making comments and suggestions for future uploads.

Enjoy!
